msgid "``/db/_revs_diff``"
msgstr ""

# 78f289ab97904cfda30ffa38f5b711af
#: ../../../src/api/database/misc.rst:191
msgid "Given a set of document/revision IDs, returns the subset of those that do not correspond to revisions stored in the database."
msgstr ""

# 38cf1635af604717b6f80863596ffbc3
#: ../../../src/api/database/misc.rst:194
msgid "Its primary use is by the replicator, as an important optimization: after receiving a set of new revision IDs from the source database, the replicator sends this set to the destination database's ``_revs_diff`` to find out which of them already exist there. It can then avoid fetching and sending already-known document bodies."
msgstr ""

